Blanco Says Spain Won’t Compensate Regions That Block Wealth Tax

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-09-16T12:13:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/blanco-says-spain-won-t-compensate-regions-that-block-wealth-tax.html
Spain ’s central government won’t
compensate regional administrations that decide not to implement
the wealth tax re-introduced by the government today, Jose
Blanco, public works minister and cabinet spokesman, said.  The government had been compensating regions for lost
revenues since it scrapped the wealth tax in 2008.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
